0:{"rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","$L2",null,{"content":{"hero_eyebrow":"Pricing","hero_heading":"Honest pricing for serious training","hero_body":"<p>Coaching education is an investment in a career that can last decades. We set our prices plainly, with no hidden fees, because you deserve to know exactly what you are committing to before you begin.</p>","table_note":"<p>Pricing table rows are read from the Credentials page. All prices are in INR and exclusive of GST.</p>","table_section_heading":"The Mastery Pathway","price_row_1_level":"Level 1: Catalyst","price_row_1_credential":"(ICI-C)","price_row_1_format":"Online, one-to-one","price_row_1_hours":"36 hours: 12 coaching + 24 self-work.","price_row_1_duration":"Up to 3 months","price_row_1_price_inr":"215000","price_row_2_level":"Level 2: Architect","price_row_2_credential":"(ICI-A)","price_row_2_format":"Online, one-to-one","price_row_2_hours":"60 hours: 20 coaching + 40 self-work.","price_row_2_duration":"Up to 4 months","price_row_2_price_inr":"345000","price_row_3_level":"Level 3: Sage","price_row_3_credential":"(ICI-S)","price_row_3_format":"Online, one-to-one","price_row_3_hours":"90 hours: 30 coaching + 60 self-work.","price_row_3_duration":"Up to 6 months","price_row_3_price_inr":"495000","price_row_4_level":"Level 4: Luminary","price_row_4_credential":"(ICI-L)","price_row_4_format":"Online, one-to-one","price_row_4_hours":"120 hours: 40 live + 80 self-work and capstone.","price_row_4_duration":"Up to 12 months","price_row_4_price_inr":"695000","includes_heading":"What every price includes","include_1":"One-to-one coaching with an experienced faculty coach","include_2":"All course materials and guided self-work","include_3":"Assessment on real coaching, not attendance","include_4":"Your ICI credential and post-nominals for life","include_5":"Membership of the ICI coaching community","enrolment_heading":"How enrolment works","enrolment_step_1":"Choose your level, or take the free assessment if you are unsure.","enrolment_step_2":"Speak with an advisor to confirm the right fit and answer your questions.","enrolment_step_3":"Confirm your place and complete enrolment, in full or by instalments.","enrolment_step_4":"Get matched with your coach and begin within 7 working days.","payment_options_heading":"Payment options","payment_options_body":"<p>Pay in full or by instalments. We will confirm the options available for your level when you speak with an advisor.</p>","gst_heading":"GST and international clients","gst_note":"<p>All prices are exclusive of GST. Applicable taxes will be added at checkout.</p>","faq_heading":"Frequently asked questions","faq_1_question":"Do I have to complete all four levels?","faq_1_answer":"<p>No. Each level is a complete certification in its own right. Many coaches stop at Catalyst or Architect. The higher levels are there when, and if, you want them.</p>","faq_2_question":"Is it really one-to-one?","faq_2_answer":"<p>Yes. You are coached and developed individually. That is the heart of the ICI model and the reason our coaches are ready for real clients.</p>","faq_3_question":"What is your refund policy?","faq_3_answer":"<p>All enrolments and payments are final. Due to the intensive, one-to-one nature of our coaching and the limited availability of our faculty, once a payment has been successfully processed, it is strictly non-refundable under any circumstances.</p>","faq_4_question":"Can I transfer my enrolment to someone else?","faq_4_answer":"No. Because each pathway is highly individualised and tailored to the specific coach's development, enrolments and payments are strictly non-transferable to another individual.","faq_5_question":"What happens if I face an emergency and cannot continue?","faq_5_answer":"While payments remain non-refundable, we understand that unforeseen emergencies arise. You may submit a formal request to pause your current training level. If approved, you can resume your sessions at a later date within the programme's suggested duration, subject to faculty availability.","faq_6_question":"Are there any exceptions to the non-refundable policy?","faq_6_answer":"No. To maintain the integrity of our scheduling and the deep commitment required for one-to-one professional coaching, the non-refundable policy applies universally without exception. We encourage you to consult with an advisor to ensure the pathway is right for you before enrolling.","cta_heading":"Ready to begin your journey?","cta_button_1_text":"Choose your level","cta_button_1_link":"/credentials","cta_button_2_text":"Take the free assessment","cta_button_2_link":"/admissions/assessment","custom_code":""}}],null,"$L3"]}],"isPartial":false,"staleTime":300,"varyParams":null,"buildId":"E38Y-g6g7OWlq8N8CNohx"}
